Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
40 Cameron Avenue in Belconnen is a refurbished A grade building surrounded by excellent amenity. The following refurbishments have now been complete; revitalised foyer and newly built business lounge, new state of the art End of Trip Facilities and on floor lift lobbies. The building foyer, business lounge and caf√© also has access to free wifi for building occupants and guests to connect.

40 Cameron Avenue positions itself as one of Australia's most financially compelling buildings to lease for discerning tenants. Currently home to a variety of occupiers including the Commonwealth of Australia and major private sector groups in the IT and health sectors.

Last remaining availability:

Level 2: 166 sqm approx*
- New fit out in place including reception, board room, office/meeting room, utility area, collaboration area and 12 work stations (with capacity for greater density)
- Access to communal high end kitchen, breakout space and meeting rooms (subject to additional charges).

*UNDER OFFER* Level 2:  530sqm* (available now, subject to vacant possession)
- Currently with fitout, or an open plan refurbished tenancy can be provided
- Excellent natural light 
- Access to modern shared facilities including break out space, meeting room and kitchen

If you are seeking quality ready to occupy accommodation in the growing town centre of Belconnen, this is the best option currently available.

For all initial enquiries please contact one of the exclusive marketing agents.
